\s KO NSHAKA GUSENGA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ko nshaka gusenga mbese ndasenga nte Mwami ntarasohora hariya mu Bwiza bwa Shekina [nshaka] nshaka gusuka amaganya yanjye imbere yawe ngirira ubuntu Mwami were kunyima amaso.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ugusenga kwanjye Mwami\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit (T) kukugereho Mukiza Ugutaka kwanjye Mwami kukugereho Mukiza Ukwinginga kwanjye Mwami kukugereho Mukiza Dor’uko mbabajwe Yesu\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit (T) Mbabarira ntunyime amaso Dor’uko nduhijwe Mwami mbabarira ntunyime amaso ndakwingize Mwami Yesu mbabarira ntunyime amaso.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Emera uko gutaka kwanjye kugere iwawe ariko kunyuriye mu maraso ya Yesu [kuko] kuko uhereye kera wanze imvugo ya bantu ariko iminiho y’Umwuka Wera ukayumva.\bd*\bd x2\bd*\bd  \bd*
